Class ExecWorker

java.lang.Object
  fig.exec.ExecWorker
All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable
public class ExecWorker
extends Object
implements Runnable

Runs on a machine. Periodically sends the master information about the worker. Contacts the execution servlet master for executions to run and runs them. Settings can be changed from the servlet. TODO: killing jobs doesn't work
